&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;ANELLO Photonics &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.anellophotonics.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Hyperlink&quot;&gt;http://www.anellophotonics.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; is a leading-edge technology company based in Santa Clara, CA. The company has developed integrated photonic system-on-chip technology for next generation navigation. ANELLO&#39;s SIPHOG™ gyroscope is based on its patented photonic integrated circuit technology. The result is a product that&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;higher performance, much smaller&amp;nbsp;size&amp;nbsp;and weight, at a fraction of the cost of traditional gyros used&amp;nbsp;for high precision&amp;nbsp;in industrial,&amp;nbsp;aerospace&amp;nbsp;and military applications. It enables reliable and&amp;nbsp;accurate&amp;nbsp;navigation and positioning in GPS-Denied environments across&amp;nbsp;autonomous&amp;nbsp;applications.&amp;nbsp;ANELLO has a growing list of customers through design wins in Commercial and Defense.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
