&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Anello Photonics:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ANELLO Photonics&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.anellophotonics.com/&quot;&gt;http://www.anellophotonics.com&lt;/a&gt; is a leading-edge technology company based in Santa Clara, CA. The company has developed an integrated photonic system-on-chip technology for next generation navigation.&amp;nbsp; ANELLO&#39;s SIPHOG™ gyroscope is based on its patented photonic integrated circuit technology. The result is a product that is higher performance, much smaller size and weight, and a fraction of the cost of traditional gyros used in industrial, aerospace and military applications. It enables reliable and accurate navigation and positioning across many autonomous applications. ANELLO is currently mid-level volume manufacturing shipping product to various market-leading customers in the Construction, Farming, Trucking, Unmanned Aerial Vehicles, Autonomous Vehicles, and National Security segments. This position will focus on our next generation offering, in R&amp;amp;D stage, that is fully funded with customers in place for high volume production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform advanced design, tolerancing, and FEA analysis for strain, vibrational nodes, model analysis, thermal and shock analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for optical system design based on experimental and system modeling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capable of analysis of key performance metrics and derive tolerance errors and mechanical tolerance analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assemble, qualify, and debug new optical-mechanical module systems and subsystems, including light source, lens system and detection sensor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop optical tooling and fixture to assist high-precision alignment and assembling process - Establish optical subsystem build and qualification process and release reliable process to Manufacturing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the Manufacturing department &amp;amp; supplier to support volume ramp and optical quality control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s Degree plus 6+ years of working experience in the field + Master’s Degree and Ph.D. Mechanical and/or Optical Engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience w/CAD package, preferably Solidworks, Ansys, including FEA (Zemax exp a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid knowledge of optical system, optical design and optical material&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good experience and design skillset with opto mechanical assemblies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong hands-on skill set on assembling, testing and troubleshooting capability with optical system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good experience with optical element vendors and design house for new product development as well as ramping up volume production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work effectively as a team player with other functional team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable and independent work style, highly accountable and responsible for the outputs&#39;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional information:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Candidates must be US Persons (US Permanent Residents or US Citizens) to be considered for jobs at ANELLO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ANELLO does not accept unsolicited resumes from recruiters or employment agencies.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About ANELLO:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;ANELLO Photonics is a Silicon Valley-based technology company pioneering high-performance inertial navigation solutions using integrated silicon photonics. Our breakthrough optical gyroscope technology enables precise navigation in GPS-denied and contested environments, supporting next-generation autonomous systems across defense&amp;nbsp;(Land,&amp;nbsp;Air and Sea)&amp;nbsp;and industrial markets.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Position Overview:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;ANELLO is seeking a senior business development leader to drive U.S. government&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;Defense&amp;nbsp;programs&amp;nbsp;and strategic growth initiatives aligned with the rapid transition to autonomous and uncrewed systems. This role will lead&amp;nbsp;engagements&amp;nbsp;with DoD, defense primes, federal agencies and&amp;nbsp;direct to&amp;nbsp;customers to position ANELLO’s navigation solutions as critical infrastructure for GPS-denied operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate brings deep experience navigating government acquisition processes, shaping requirements, and winning funding proposals and customer design wins—particularly in autonomy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;1. Government Strategy &amp;amp; Capture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Develop and execute U.S. government business development and capture strategy across DoD (Navy, Army, Air Force,&amp;nbsp;Marines,&amp;nbsp;SOCOM,&amp;nbsp;DIU&amp;nbsp;etc)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Identify, qualify, and lead capture of programs in autonomy, uncrewed systems (USV/UUV/UAS/UGV), and GPS&amp;nbsp;denied precision navigation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Shape early-stage requirements and influence program definitions through direct engagement with program offices and stakeholders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Drive system-level design wins with primes and integrators delivering autonomous platforms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
